item.title: Wiki Redux Recruiting
item.content:encoded:
Wiki Redux Village, the remnants of The Wiki Village is looking to recruit about 10-15 people. We're an immortal realm village, already in the NRF, and very well could be Epic tomorrow if we had the people.

Wiki Redux is also the official village of this site.
